data.description: Beautiful-MUST SEE 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath, 1780 SF, 2-Car Garage home located in the Gated Community of Clearwater; in the Desirable City of Bonney Lake!! The main level features vaulted Ceilings, w/an open-concept floorplan, a Family room, a Formal Dining Area, a Kitchen w/eating area, a 1/2 bath, a utility room, private, spacious Fully fenced back yard. Upstairs offers 3 bedrooms, a Spacious Master Bath, and two walk-in closets with peek-a-boo views of Mt. Rainier from the bedroom upstairs, newer Roof, Carpet, and Exterior Painting! Spacious backyard, perfect for entertaining! Shed stays! This home is Move-In-READY, and has everything you need! All appliances stay! Close to HWY 410, shopping, restaurants, and schools.
